text: Babayevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Kameyevsky Selsoviet, Mishkinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 190 as of 2010. There are 5 streets. == Geography == It is located 16 km from Mishkino, 4 km from Kameyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Mishkinsky District
title: Babayevo, Mishkinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
